overview.en: IP5G is a high-tech public chain based on blockchain technology jointly created by the world's top blockchain technology team and 5G technology team. At the same time, it is a global and open blockchain ecosystem with blockchain technology as the bottom layer. system.
overview.zh: IP5G，是由世界顶尖的区块链技术团队与5G技术团队联合打造一款基于区块链技术的高科技公链，同时是以区块链技术为底层的全球化、开放式区块链生态系统。
